This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with 3D object detection using monocular RGB-only approaches. Additionally, robotics (cs.RO) is also a likely sub-category as the paper discusses the use of LiDAR and stereo camera rigs in comparison to their proposed method. Machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) are also possible sub-categories as the paper discusses the use of a deep learning architecture. Finally, natural language processing (cs.CL) is a less likely sub-category as it is not directly related to the content of the paper.
